CPSC589 Assignment 1

Keyboard controls:

	SPACE 		- toggle animation
	LEFT ARROW 	- shrink radius of inner circle  (>0 minimum)
	RIGHT ARROW - grow radius of inner circle	(outer circle radius is max)
	UP ARROW 	- grow radius of outer circle
	DOWN ARROW 	- shrink radius of outer circle  (inner circle radius is min)
	A			- rotate counter-clockwise
	D			- rotate clockwise
	W			- increase scale 
	S			- decrease scale  (0 minimum)
	+			- increase cycles
	-			- decrease cycles  (1 minimum)
	ESCAPE		- exit program
	
User can press and hold keys to modify the hypocycloid values.  

Bonus:  Start/stop the animation by pressing SPACE.

Files submitted:

	README
	main.cpp
	point3D.h
	makefile
